{"id":593327,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/费说新语│红朝见闻录（二十七）/","date":"2018-08-18T17:03:28Z","modified":"2018-08-18T17:03:28Z","title":"费说新语│红朝见闻录（二十七）","content":"<div id=\"page-content\" class=\"rich_media_area_primary\">\n<div class=\"rich_media_area_primary_inner\">\n<div id=\"img-content\">\n<div id=\"js_content\" class=\"rich_media_content \">\n<section>\n<section>撰写 湖州老费 │ 编辑 贵群群主</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">1</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>商量出处到红裙</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>某友，雅好书画鉴赏，圈内很有些名声。一般向其请教，话不多，使人莫测高深。但有美女在侧就例外，滔滔不绝，非但不问自答，还根本不让旁人插嘴。今晚急匆匆微信我说有个篆刻名家答应刻方闲章送他，让我帮想一个既不失高雅又切合他身份的内容。我说龚定𥂝有一句诗，很适合你，叫“商量出处到红裙”。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">2</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>杂志</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>《X华X才》是我唯一订了很久的杂志，无关励志，只是想了解新近又出了哪几路骗子。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">3</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>拉黑帝</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>本以为赵老师拉黑了微信大多数朋友，是想在喧嚣的世界里守住一份寂寞。见他居然还郑重其事写了篇数千字文章告白天下，就有点不甘寂寞了。突然想起不知哪位前辈讲过的一段话：人害怕寂寞，害怕到无耻的程度，换言之，人的某些无耻行径是由于害怕寂寞而做出来的。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">4</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>长短人</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>随园诗话：“高青丘笑古人作诗，今人描诗。描诗者，像生花之类，所谓优孟衣冠，诗中之乡愿也。”长沙谭伯牛兄说：“前人称填词为长短句，当下写诗的，可叫作长短人。”</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">5</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>治便秘</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>被一个佛系美女怒怼，我不是佛教徒，别说当下那些开班授徒的名僧大德对佛教奥义一知半解，即便在佛教盛行的魏晋南北朝和唐时代，底层教众也就是一个愚昧和迷信的群体。阿城老师《闲话闲说》：“大英博物馆藏的敦煌卷子里，记着一条女供养人的祈祷，求佛祖保佑自己的丈夫拉出屎来，因为他大便干燥，痛苦万分。”治便秘，还是我朋友曾总引进的杜邦益生菌固体饮料最见效。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">6</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>祖上曾阔过</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>地方文化的宣传套路，就是“天地奇气，必有所钟，畸人杰士，不绝于世”，其反复想证明的便是鲁迅说的“祖上也曾阔过”。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">7</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>气壮才能理直</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>“三月十五日，兆铭自被捕后再次受审，作供词洋洋数千言，当得起理直气壮四个字。”有网友说，世道变了，现在理直就不一定气壮，而是气壮才能理直。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">8</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>没读过书</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>“我是个中国人。对于中国文化，我用全部的身心去理解。越接近它，越觉其深不可测，越是敬畏。”大凡说这种话的人，无一例外是没有读过什么书的。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">9</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>低级骗术</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>一落座，朋友介绍居中一位西装革履干部模样的人说是李教授、博导、国学大师。寒喧几句，大师递过一沓印制精美的文件，扫了一眼封面，是几份申遗的策划书。我推说另外还有事，就先起身告辞。朋友送到门口，问我是不是从前认识大师，有过节？我说那倒不是，只是觉得此人甚是过分，初次见面就表演这种低级的骗术，辱人智商。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">10</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>卡夫卡</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>卡夫卡说：“要客观地看待自己的痛苦！”但又有多少人会客观地看待自己的辉煌呢？</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">11</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>看新闻联播</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>股票跌惨了，老杨长叹短吁，吃饭也没有心思。有朋友说：“炒股票，还应该多关心中国政治。”老杨沉默了一会，起身离席。问他干嘛这么早走？老杨说：“回家看新闻联播去。”</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">12</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>得体</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>人之间的交流，得体最为要紧。男人女腔，土豪装雅士，科员局长口气，家丁员外派头，民主党派作共/产/党/员状，都十分不可耐。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">13</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>穿了裤子没法飞</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>听靖江梁朝伟讲回乡故事，讲河那边的王祖贤，讲和表弟喝了一箱啤酒，乘兴在乡间的小路上裸奔，阵阵凉风穿裆吹过，有冯虚御风的感觉。最后从他的历史学专业角度发出一声感叹，人类自从穿上了裤子，就再也飞不起来了。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">14</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>私智小慧</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>饭间一桌人的话题都集中在目前经济形势下个人资产的安全问题，有认为要赶紧兑美元的，有认为继续买房产的，激进点的，不惜代价要移民。我默坐许久，本不想说什么，但还是禁不住大家催问，只好如实说这些办法，都属于被猪圈长期限制了智商以后的私智小慧，解决不了根本问题。大家又追问我有什么好办法，我说我真的不敢讲……</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">15</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>美帝亡我之心不死</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>存目。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">16</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>自负与绝望</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>半夜翻翻朋友圈，艺术家大多自负，知识分子普遍绝望。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">17</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>连襟十余个</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>朋友圈一女的，平时也就发发美食，发发自拍，发发菩萨保佑之类。这半年增加了一项新内容，动不动就“感恩亲爱的老公，是你的爱滋润了我，是你伴陪我走过这五年的静好岁月”云云。我没忍住，说这些话枕头边说去！她就把我拉黑了。昨天偶然听朋友说起，这女的老公假装出差一月，在家偷偷装了监控设备，二十天拍到连襟十余个。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">18</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>激烈与平和</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>说起时事，过去我算是最激烈的。最近三个月，突然发现身边无论体制内体制外，得益者还是未得益者，说话个个比我激烈，我算是非常平和的了。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">29</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>贸易战</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>存目。</p>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section class=\"\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<p class=\"\" title=\"\">20</p>\n</section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class=\"\">\n<section><strong>不知耻者更勇</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<p>子曰：知耻近乎勇。</p>\n<p>茅大为先生说：不知耻者更勇。</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"js_toobar3\" class=\"rich_media_tool\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rich_media_area_extra\">\n<div class=\"rich_media_area_extra_inner\">\n<div id=\"js_share_appmsg\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"js_pc_qr_code\" class=\"qr_code_pc_outer\">\n<div class=\"qr_code_pc_inner\"></div>\n</div>\n","author":1057,"categories":[18270,18269,9203],"tags":[12232,17155,35778,28564,10205]}